  "text_content": "Greetings from Auroville, the City of Dawn Auroville was inaugurated on February 28th, 1968, in the presence of 5000 people Youth representing 124 Nations participated in the inauguration of Auroville To build an ideal society, an ideal city Greetings from Auroville to all men of good will. Are invited to Auroville all those who thirst for progress and aspire to a higher and truer life. Savitri Bhavan is a centre dedicated to the works of Sri Aurobindo and the Mother (HOMA) At present, Auroville is a growing community of over 3300 people from 60 nations... ‹ › ‹ › ‹ › ‹ › ‹ › ‹ › ‹ › • • • • • • • Auroville wants to be a universal town where men and women of all countries are able to live in peace and progressive harmony above all creeds, all politics and all nationalities. The purpose of Auroville is to realize human unity. The Visitors Centre, the Matrimandir Viewing Point, and the Inner Chamber Are Open to Visitors Matrimandir Website : matrimandir.org The Matrimandir Viewing Point for Visitors : Find more details here New link: matrimandir.org/how-to-visit/ The Matrimandir Inner Chamber: The Inner Chamber is open to visitors daily except on Tuesdays and Sundays. Learn how to visit the Inner Chamber: https://matrimandir.org/how-to-visit/#booking Guidelines for Auroville Residents and Registered Volunteers, for access to the Inner Chamber, are mentioned here. Auroville: The City of Dawn The purpose of Auroville is to realise human unity - in diversity. Today Auroville is recognised as the first and only internationally endorsed ongoing experiment in human unity and transformation of consciousness. Learn About Auroville Visit & Stay in Auroville Auroville has so much more to offer than meets the eye at first glance; it is all about a different way of living and receiving the world. Depending on how much time you are planning to spend at Auroville, there are different possibilites. Visit & Stay Joining Auroville Discover Matrimandir Auroville's Guiding Principles Volunteering in Auroville Workshops & Therapies Auroville Products Featured Pages Matrimandir - The Soul of the City Frequently Asked Questions on Coming to Auroville Georges Van Vrekhem Auroville International Integral Health and Wellness Auroville Passings The Founders of Auroville Auroville Live What’s New Admission and Termination ATR & ATSC People of Auroville Census 2025 - Auroville Population Kinisi Cowork DONATE TOWARDS AUROVILLE Support the City of Dawn Despite the huge progress that Auroville has made, there are certain critical areas where help is needed urgently. Auroville is grateful for your generous support to help build the City of Dawn. Donate Donation Guidelines Auroville Radio Facebook Page News & Events in Auroville News & Notes Auroville Today Magazine Regular Events in Auroville Enlight - Workshops Statements of Support & Testimonials Government of India UNESCO Dalai Lama Others",
